I have already figured that out!! SCARY.
I was high on Lortab because I have a very bad tooth that is getting a crown
this next week and had so much pain I could not function. I was at ebay, my
head nodding, my lids closing, but still chasing those auctions about to end!!!
Crazy...just couldn't stop though.

Ren
